Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個裝置是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繭利大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繭利大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 你想來抓我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繭利大人 您這是干什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術開發局 第七研究塔內部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現異常靈壓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼人正在實驗塔頂層
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行破壞活動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超高濃度靈子雲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在這附近一帶擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重復一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求護廷十三隊全隊 以及鬼道眾進行支援...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作要快 可惡..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅隊長 請快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別接近我 你們想要怎麼處置我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 終於瘋掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將你的存在..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜靈庭被..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃往高處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是活該
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好死神們都全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們總是在失去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他們總是在奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙從剛剛開始在干什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在讀大姐的便條呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像暗號一樣 根本搞不懂其中的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,buyokauji....gabude....ki...to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提示就是這張畫嗎 這是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少來挑剔大姐這藝術般的畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊 話說你口中的大姐是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？大姐就是大姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙在說什麼呢 在犯傻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯傻的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天先睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這家伙...再陪我一會兒啊 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 一護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會道謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要成為死神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什麼啊 突然就..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這像蟑螂一樣的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊畫著西瓜也就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想玩獨角仙嗎 就是說..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有急事..先回屍魂界了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天就回來 你們乖乖等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋們 露琪亞...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍魂界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾啦 小雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你是..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽木露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 朽木露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 露琪亞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你這裡的老主顧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們店的老主顧嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 確實有這個名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對不起 我真的不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你不也有一瞬間忘掉了大姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..雖說不知道是否和你說的這位露琪亞有關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實昨晚靜靈庭發生了令人難以置信的變故
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變故？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二番隊隊長涅繭利發生錯亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞了設施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此造成靜靈庭的三分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像正處於毀滅的邊緣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是這兩件事有所關聯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是導致我們的記憶發生混亂的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情是不是就是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你和這位露琪亞的關系是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我珍視的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我深愛的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧 一護 去屍魂界 Let's Go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 浦原先生 拜托你准備穿界門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異常靈子的流出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已經趨於平穩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護廷十三隊各隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了查明原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始在庭內展開部署了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一護 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快 快看 這 這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是開什麼玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有全軍覆沒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長們自不必說..其他人就..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐她 大姐她沒事吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩人 別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先尋找露琪亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門被關閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群礙事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰過面而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檜佐木大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百步欄杆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你們別逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和露琪亞一起走 我們的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 剛剛那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 大家這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個假面 你是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一護 你們不是認識的嗎 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檜佐木大哥 是我 黑崎一護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他 是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的旅禍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 一護 雖然搞不清狀況 不過應該很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檜佐木大哥 我不想和你打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的旅禍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿散井 別讓他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是你干的好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 是我啊 一護啊 不認識了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡亂說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 戀次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和你打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙為何知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 戀次 露琪亞有危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙從剛才開始就在亂說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你連露琪亞都不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會忘記她呢 是不是啊 戀次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼不著邊際的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊跟阿散井 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這裡要..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狛村隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要抓緊了 好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卍解 黑繩天譴明王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大家伙是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月牙天衝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的水還給我 看我宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戌吊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給她看清楚臉的話 她是記不起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 快看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告損害狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流出靈子造成的損害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以東西方向為中心二百靈裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波及到靜靈庭內全境的三成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷者狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前所未有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被靈子纏繞 好像被石化了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處於連生死都無法確認的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看來還有很多方面沒有搞清..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是現狀 還是自己本身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像失去了一部分記憶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狛村隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和身份不明的穿著死霸裝的旅禍交戰過了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 旅禍擁有虛一般的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為其靈壓足以匹敵隊長級別
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且還有一些難以理解的事情..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對我們十分了解 朽木隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對阿散井副隊長還報上了自己的姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和副隊長進行了交談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於此事 阿散井的報告是完全不認識此人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事情 我本身也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情陷於窘境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可謂是靜靈庭創建以來的重大事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各隊配合火速搜尋並擒拿旅禍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起 不要殺我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是地下水道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在這裡打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你就突然從天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的治療還是一如既往的出色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 你認識我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 之前好像也幫你包扎過傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 看來是我的錯覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別指望他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說..你現在肯定在煩惱什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連這也看得出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂包扎寫作漢字是[手當]意思就是掌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是通過手掌去觸摸對方的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口的疼痛 心中的傷痛 都悉數傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在此煩惱下去 也是於事無補啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受你照顧啦 花太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 露琪亞 會有精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以問你件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然認識你們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過抱歉 卻記不太清了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這封信我是何時從你們那裡收到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很能干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是模仿露琪亞你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常給我們畫的畫而畫出的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你肯定能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何不留姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:22:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有名字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是露琪亞你約定好要給我們取名的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們約定好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在現世 總是父母給孩子取名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以露琪亞你說要給我們取名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你們……取名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 濕成這樣 去干啥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 露琪亞 你說有話和我們說是什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你們沒有名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 能讓我給你們取名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無名無姓諸多不便
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 不想的話別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.61,0:23:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.19,0:23:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想讓露琪亞你來取名的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.57,0:24:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我們取名吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.99,0:24:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我早就想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 名字 名字 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.01,0:24:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 別這麼吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.07,0:24:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我那時……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.63,0:24:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是那對小姐弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.91,0:24:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的名字的是什麼啊 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.71,0:24:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有告訴你們名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.26,0:24:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 你怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.64,0:24:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.34,0:24:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我記不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.14,0:24:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.36,0:24:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在為止都在干什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.01,0:24:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.24,0:24:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在沉睡 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.61,0:25:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直睡了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.33,0:25:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.92,0:25:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你受了傷一直在沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.61,0:25:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不要急 我們會永遠在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.15,0:25:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.04,0:25:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.60,0:26:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張照片 是大姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.76,0:26:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大聲喧嘩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.47,0:26:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 擅自闖進來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.44,0:26:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想在這引發事端
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.46,0:26:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張照片是緋真小姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.86,0:26:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和露琪亞真像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.34,0:26:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定也感覺到什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.01,0:26:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.82,0:26:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.59,0:26:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋真是露琪亞的姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.49,0:26:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.39,0:26:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.51,0:26:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞是你的義妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.22,0:26:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你違背定則也要保護的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.75,0:27:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然也不記得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.63,0:27:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何知道我妻緋真的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.39,0:27:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為……
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.65,0:27:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一護
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.46,0:27:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.97,0:27:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.64,0:27:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙為何在此
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.70,0:27:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 戀次
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.47,0:27:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 怒吼吧 蛇尾丸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.83,0:27:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是這種講道理說不清的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.73,0:27:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.33,0:27:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先用身體來領教領教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.52,0:27:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卍解！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.56,0:28:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 戀次
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.13,0:28:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.87,0:28:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不卍解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.25,0:28:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我會卍解？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.94,0:28:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是為了救露琪亞而修行過的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.81,0:28:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才知道 怒吼吧 蛇尾丸
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.85,0:28:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.42,0:28:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我記起什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.91,0:28:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.00,0:28:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.78,0:28:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋真生於南流魂街78地區 戌吊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.26,0:29:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.47,0:29:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.60,0:29:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.24,0:29:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 你怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.49,0:29:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很久沒呼吸過這個城鎮的空氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.61,0:29:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於自己一無所知..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.22,0:29:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真是放不下心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.00,0:29:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.60,0:29:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直在等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.47,0:29:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時說要給你們取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.46,0:29:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會想起來的 那個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.80,0:30:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.17,0:30:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.74,0:30:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是那個山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.88,0:30:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.36,0:30:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.62,0:30:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是這種講道理說不清的人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.29,0:30:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇尾丸
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.21,0:30:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何不用卍解
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.39,0:30:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.33,0:30:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在怕什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.14,0:31:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的靈魂應該認識我的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.23,0:31:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連和我靈魂交互的事你也忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.55,0:31:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不像樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.13,0:31:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.32,0:31:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白哉大人 白哉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.43,0:31:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你去流魂街了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.48,0:31:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.04,0:31:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我並不是在責怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.35,0:31:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是擔心你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.74,0:31:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白哉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.40,0:31:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這個要請你……
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.42,0:31:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋真
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.32,0:31:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 白哉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.74,0:32:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 不要太逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.15,0:32:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我一定要去找
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算身體有什麼萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.75,0:32:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去找什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.94,0:32:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告 白道門被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.17,0:32:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是旅禍干的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.55,0:32:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 十番隊以及勇敢志士
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.70,0:32:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所組成的討伐隊已經出動追擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.41,0:33:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為何旅禍占盡地利
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.50,0:33:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.61,0:33:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐真的在這裡生活過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.81,0:33:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.87,0:33:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐怎麼可能在..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.52,0:33:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.35,0:33:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.47,0:34:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我就是在這裡和同伴們一起長大 然後
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.68,0:34:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.76,0:34:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.09,0:34:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.74,0:34:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.96,0:34:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.24,0:34:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.50,0:34:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.38,0:34:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.04,0:34:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.26,0:34:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何在此
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.16,0:34:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.50,0:34:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.62,0:34:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們退下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.29,0:34:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要問你是何人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.48,0:34:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.21,0:34:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 你應該記得我吧 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.35,0:34:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 可疑的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.42,0:35:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…疑的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.90,0:35:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.15,0:35:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.84,0:35:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 露琪亞 是我啊 一護啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.12,0:35:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.01,0:35:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.21,0:35:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那家伙的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.54,0:35:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.68,0:35:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然干什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.78,0:35:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.92,0:35:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 干掉這死神
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.42,0:35:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都叫你住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.37,0:35:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.16,0:35:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是瞬步啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.95,0:35:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.10,0:35:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.18,0:36:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那感覺是……
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.42,0:36:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過了斬月
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.02,0:36:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 喂 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.88,0:36:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.47,0:36:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.23,0:36:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是來了一位久違的熟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.88,0:36:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是百年不變一張惹人厭的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.19,0:36:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你還記得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.38,0:36:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.82,0:37:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會只是為了確認這個
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.34,0:37:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而專程來到這裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.42,0:37:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是 我想稍微調查一下你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.80,0:37:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.60,0:37:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.18,0:37:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一開始是你出現混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.36,0:37:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們對某個人的記憶就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.99,0:37:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.04,0:37:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.16,0:37:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你與那個人 都遇到了同一個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.05,0:37:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.91,0:37:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.72,0:37:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才從你房間找出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.49,0:37:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在的你 估計連這個都不記得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.34,0:38:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧 為了奪回一切
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.54,0:38:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼想 這一連串的騷動都是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.68,0:38:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那些奇怪的家伙搞出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.44,0:38:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐也被掠走了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.88,0:38:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是居然連大姐也忘了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.65,0:38:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛的不是傷 是心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.37,0:38:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也說點什麼啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.52,0:38:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.64,0:38:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一樣 露琪亞也是 戀次也是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.62,0:38:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們眼中都沒有我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.71,0:38:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為他們只是不記得露琪亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.07,0:38:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.80,0:38:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看錯你啦 一護 你泄什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.35,0:38:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撞到頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.68,0:38:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在現世也發現了大姐身處險境
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.49,0:38:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算大家都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.87,0:39:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也沒有忘記大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.65,0:39:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和大姐還有羈絆的維繫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.59,0:39:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我一個人也要救出大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.53,0:39:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算大姐忘了我 我也不管
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.76,0:39:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在那裡一直用你那
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.37,0:39:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨拙的腦袋繼續想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.40,0:39:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙算什麼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.35,0:39:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.79,0:39:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.36,0:39:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我認識那個死神
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.20,0:39:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我並不是一直沉睡著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.83,0:39:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在為止究竟做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.80,0:39:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何認識那個死神
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.99,0:39:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.13,0:39:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.27,0:39:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.19,0:40:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.36,0:40:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們去了很遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.12,0:40:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遠的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.92,0:40:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.53,0:40:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了見露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.38,0:40:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然花了將近100年的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.90,0:40:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼久...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.96,0:40:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 露琪亞...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.59,0:40:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神他們 都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.82,0:40:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了奪取而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.91,0:40:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那群家伙什麼都奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.95,0:40:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心的事情 愉快的事情 還有露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.97,0:40:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.86,0:40:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.29,0:40:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.24,0:40:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.18,0:41:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.36,0:41:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.38,0:41:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.54,0:41:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.98,0:41:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.05,0:41:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒看呢 所以我才在問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.07,0:41:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就敬請期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.86,0:41:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我找了好久都沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.51,0:41:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候把姐姐送我的情書給....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.26,0:41:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 對你這種沒骨氣的家伙來說太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.60,0:41:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.58,0:42:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.16,0:42:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.38,0:42:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 竟然還要你教我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.88,0:42:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也還差得遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.75,0:42:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.23,0:42:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋裝什麼酷
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.44,0:42:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我改好重新說
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.72,0:42:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.05,0:42:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.38,0:42:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.70,0:42:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.14,0:42:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你開始不是有一陣忘掉了大姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.22,0:42:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是我和大姐的羈絆比較深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.48,0:42:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓你逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.68,0:42:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你乖乖束手就擒吧 旅禍們
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.32,0:42:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是小題大做啊 冬獅郎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.68,0:42:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.19,0:42:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道日番谷隊長的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.83,0:42:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.54,0:42:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一角
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.72,0:43:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓親
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.71,0:43:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.43,0:43:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們不記得我了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.34,0:43:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.96,0:43:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是旅禍的胡言亂語罷了 一角
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.29,0:43:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.93,0:43:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神代理 黑崎一護
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.54,0:43:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是死神代理？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.05,0:43:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就把證據拿出來瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.43,0:43:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.77,0:44:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 斑目 我上
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.40,0:44:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來果真和報告的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.50,0:44:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是了解我們的戰鬥方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.90,0:44:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再問你一次 你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.92,0:44:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了我是黑崎一護了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.63,0:44:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒印象
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.86,0:44:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縛道之六十三 鎖條鎖縛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.39,0:44:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒吼吧 蛇尾丸
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.16,0:44:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.80,0:45:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思 阿散井
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.00,0:45:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.89,0:45:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀次？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.74,0:45:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別直呼我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.86,0:45:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.61,0:45:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是擾亂靜靈庭的旅禍
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.62,0:45:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.65,0:45:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.84,0:45:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是無法將你視為敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.02,0:45:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然腦子裡明白你是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.14,0:45:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我的靈魂...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.30,0:45:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻告訴我你不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.51,0:45:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我決定遵從我的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.90,0:45:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿散井
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.73,0:45:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 日番谷隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.22,0:45:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我們通過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.53,0:46:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許有人背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.12,0:46:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.27,0:46:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要擒獲旅禍
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.27,0:46:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您聽我說 總隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.77,0:46:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 說出來就能互相理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.87,0:46:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多言
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.30,0:46:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擒拿他們 是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.80,0:47:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.62,0:47:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個身影是...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.07,0:47:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦原喜助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.68,0:47:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦原先生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.24,0:47:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 總隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.91,0:47:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.52,0:47:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神們還被圍困呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.13,0:47:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.04,0:47:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.73,0:47:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得有些太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.26,0:47:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去露琪亞...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.15,0:47:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會永遠記不起我們的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.03,0:47:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.17,0:47:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.32,0:47:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.83,0:48:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕不能讓她想起那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.19,0:48:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想起來了我們就...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.74,0:48:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.69,0:48:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 只要殺光所有死神
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.91,0:48:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞就會永遠和我們在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.13,0:48:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想不起我們的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.26,0:48:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.54,0:48:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何要回來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.11,0:48:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是沒有任何線索的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.44,0:48:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來向您彙報一下
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.54,0:48:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所言何事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.40,0:48:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指的是重要事件
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.21,0:48:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和叛徒沒什麼好談的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.64,0:48:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼著急嘛 碎蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.50,0:48:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜一大人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.36,0:48:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是不是忘記了重要的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.05,0:48:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼重要事情
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.46,0:49:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我一直寢食不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.39,0:49:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您務必告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.12,0:49:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.74,0:49:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.01,0:49:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說元凶？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.26,0:49:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不過在此之前 黑崎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.46,0:49:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然涅和露琪亞都被同樣的敵人奪走了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.44,0:49:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.72,0:49:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拿著大鐮刀的二人組嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.04,0:49:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有過接觸了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.21,0:49:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就事不宜遲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.94,0:49:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事情就交給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.47,0:49:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快去追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.71,0:49:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.92,0:49:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.39,0:49:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走 戀次
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.91,0:49:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說 別直呼我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.87,0:49:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.07,0:49:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家應該也隱約察覺到一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.96,0:49:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種說不出的不協調感
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.58,0:49:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像忘了什麼很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.46,0:49:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種不安的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.32,0:50:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此 在這靜靈庭危難之時
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.55,0:50:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會為了區區旅禍不惜至此
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.68,0:50:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是這樣嗎 總隊長閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.43,0:50:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.60,0:50:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.56,0:50:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是要找到露琪亞了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.65,0:50:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在問她是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.10,0:50:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是露琪亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.56,0:50:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒想起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.72,0:50:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是和她走得最近的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.62,0:50:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識好久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.67,0:50:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.10,0:50:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊 我不記得了 要水嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.14,0:50:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.72,0:50:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算便宜點哦 要不要純淨的水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.94,0:50:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 戀次
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.82,0:50:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的水還給我 小心我宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.30,0:50:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.81,0:51:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.31,0:51:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.86,0:51:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念100遍也好 200遍也好給我想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.49,0:51:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問你件事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.81,0:51:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼為那家伙能做到這地步
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.34,0:51:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要救露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.89,0:51:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 那家伙改變了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.28,0:51:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救瀕死的我和我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.41,0:51:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她將死神的力量分給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.08,0:51:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.17,0:51:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是拜她所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.89,0:52:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們身上到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.41,0:52:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用一句話說
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.06,0:52:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們記憶的一部分被抹去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.21,0:52:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我按順序解釋下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.92,0:52:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在技術開發局剛成立不久時
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.25,0:52:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經研究過一個虛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.54,0:52:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它寄生於魂魄 奪取魂魄的意識維持生存
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.80,0:52:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而當其身體逐漸衰弱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.34,0:52:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就轉而寄生到其他身體之上
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.76,0:52:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 最不可思議的是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.22,0:52:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄生時所使用的像鐮刀一樣的觸手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.19,0:52:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將對方記憶抹除
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.63,0:52:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這家伙將朽木露琪亞這個死神
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.76,0:52:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關死神的全部記憶都抹除的話
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.98,0:52:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認為會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.01,0:52:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事 不可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.60,0:52:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙的能力確實
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.86,0:53:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充其量只能寄生於靈力很弱的魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.48,0:53:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹去記憶也只是短暫的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.14,0:53:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難想像它能夠將一個死神的存在本身完全抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.39,0:53:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.87,0:53:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若有什麼其他的力量注入其中的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.36,0:53:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想說這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.81,0:53:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.31,0:53:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶是連接在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.61,0:53:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說成是羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.75,0:53:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果一個人的記憶全被抹除掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.52,0:53:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼同時 周圍的人的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.87,0:53:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和有關此人的全部信息都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.07,0:53:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這次出現了一個特例
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.91,0:53:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才那個叫黑崎的男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.37,0:53:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.68,0:53:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎的死神力量 本來就是朽木露琪亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.41,0:53:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們連黑崎的事情也都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.89,0:53:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神的力量竟然會轉移？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.84,0:53:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下如此的重罪..
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.26,0:53:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 正如您所說
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.52,0:54:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們已經接受了黑崎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.61,0:54:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以抵消這重罪的恩惠了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.48,0:54:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是將這樣一個人徹底的忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.74,0:54:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也將他給忘記了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.66,0:54:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我還留有一些記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.19,0:54:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒釀成大錯
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.42,0:54:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.90,0:54:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅的事情又怎麼解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.48,0:54:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙我們可是都還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.39,0:54:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在這
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.86,0:54:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想不通這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.10,0:54:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過正如你們所知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.16,0:54:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅隊長是個很奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.36,0:54:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他對自己做過些什麼也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.10,0:54:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我照這個思路去調查了一下 果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.22,0:54:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅隊長經常會存留自己記憶的備份
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.80,0:54:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 托他的福
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.60,0:54:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家才沒有忘記他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.78,0:55:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.70,0:55:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的記憶都是連接在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.13,0:55:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 魂 知道露琪亞的下落了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.76,0:55:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.30,0:55:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說靜靈庭也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.18,0:55:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道大姐不久前曾經在這裡通過
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.35,0:55:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.38,0:55:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.09,0:55:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.56,0:55:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說你的死神力量是從露琪亞那得到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.39,0:55:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.93,0:55:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也許靈質很接近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.09,0:55:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說也許可以憑借靈絡找到她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.02,0:55:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈絡？我找她恐怕不行
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.92,0:55:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實在這個由靈子構成的屍魂界內
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.53,0:55:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要看到視覺化的靈脈一般做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.10,0:55:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.46,0:55:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈質接近的你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.02,0:55:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許能夠找到露琪亞殘留的靈絡
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.15,0:55:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然也不擅長這方面的鬼道
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.51,0:56:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是可以幫你 快試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.56,0:56:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知不行也要試試
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.83,0:56:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.13,0:56:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種明知不行的心態能成功才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.45,0:56:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她..露琪亞和我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.36,0:56:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是連在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.01,0:56:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要找到她的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.99,0:56:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.11,0:56:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.46,0:57:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能運轉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.02,0:57:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.16,0:57:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.26,0:57:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.74,0:57:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.26,0:57:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭還疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.71,0:57:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.16,0:57:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.31,0:57:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將那些使露琪亞痛苦的死神全部趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.24,0:57:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓死神？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.16,0:57:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就是用這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.26,0:58:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 你們有沒有想過這樣會造成多大的損傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.37,0:58:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定靜靈庭會被完全毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.81,0:58:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.17,0:58:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要站在死神那一邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.92,0:58:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神又會來把露琪亞從我們身邊搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.47,0:58:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.09,0:58:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再和露琪亞分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.94,0:58:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.74,0:58:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們永遠都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.79,0:58:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說謊 你要相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.82,0:58:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 絕對不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.26,0:58:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要干掉他們...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.28,0:58:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.71,0:58:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 因為露琪亞...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.00,0:58:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.77,0:59:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.11,0:59:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像是開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.82,0:59:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.86,0:59:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.27,0:59:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒吼吧 蛇尾丸
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.05,0:59:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀次
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.58,0:59:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了交給我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.73,0:59:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卍解
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.91,0:59:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狒狒王蛇尾丸
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.91,1:00:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記起卍解了？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.98,1:00:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什麼 多危險啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.67,1:00:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.40,1:00:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 蛇尾丸還有這種用法呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.14,1:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.72,1:00:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意 衝啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.55,1:00:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卍解
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.49,1:00:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鎖斬月
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.25,1:00:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.61,1:00:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.52,1:01:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.25,1:01:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死神
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.15,1:01:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.94,1:01:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.85,1:01:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 我們來接你了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.26,1:01:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.83,1:01:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.58,1:01:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀次
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.74,1:01:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 滾回去死神
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.93,1:02:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞可不認識你們
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.59,1:02:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.43,1:02:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞可是我們重要的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.63,1:02:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞可不想這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.12,1:02:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞已經和你們不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.64,1:02:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.88,1:02:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所認識的你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.42,1:02:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不會隨便拋棄死神的身份
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.54,1:02:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為初次見面的我奮不顧身
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.98,1:02:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我能夠保護家人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.19,1:02:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你自己的力量分給了我
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.77,1:02:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那種堅強的人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.40,1:02:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.30,1:02:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是……
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.26,1:02:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要這樣 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.74,1:02:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別露出這種表情 我不要
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.33,1:02:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要露琪亞變回死神
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.94,1:02:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回死神？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.36,1:03:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾是死神對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.00,1:03:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.97,1:03:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再問你一次
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.96,1:03:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.57,1:03:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一護
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.76,1:03:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂大人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.32,1:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.93,1:03:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一護…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.86,1:03:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.41,1:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.44,1:03:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.09,1:03:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.95,1:04:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把露琪亞交給你們的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.71,1:04:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.92,1:04:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會交給你們
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.23,1:04:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要變成這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.86,1:04:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.27,1:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就和露琪亞合為一體
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.61,1:04:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來露琪亞也會消失
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.47,1:04:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.91,1:04:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.28,1:04:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直都要在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.89,1:04:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.16,1:04:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.43,1:04:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.87,1:04:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 大姐
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.45,1:05:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.46,1:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.81,1:05:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.47,1:05:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙就是把靜靈庭搞得一塌糊塗的元凶嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.92,1:05:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止她 戀次
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.29,1:05:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想辦法搞定那個女人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.97,1:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是為此才來這兒的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.04,1:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.64,1:06:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 大姐
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.01,1:06:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.63,1:06:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.14,1:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速速撤離
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.55,1:06:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檜佐木副隊長 松本副隊長 快看那
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.51,1:07:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊……
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.00,1:07:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.30,1:07:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,割除吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.72,1:07:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 割除他
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.47,1:08:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.52,1:08:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.02,1:08:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快清醒吧 是我 一護啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.92,1:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想起來啊 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.83,1:08:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這樣下去靜靈庭會被吞噬的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.50,1:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松本
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.42,1:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.39,1:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 松本 是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.92,1:09:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.56,1:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了個了不得的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.05,1:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據涅隊長所說 敵人應該持有他所做的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.56,1:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈子收集裝置的控制鎖
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.95,1:09:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅慘狀 是讓那東西暴走的結果
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.98,1:09:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.42,1:09:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要阻止這種失控局面 必須破壞裝置
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.97,1:09:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可對方不會讓我們輕易接近的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.72,1:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎他們已置身其中了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.83,1:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要防止庭內的靈子繼續擴散
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.91,1:09:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的真輕巧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.90,1:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前就是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.88,1:09:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森羅萬像 皆化為灰燼吧 流刃若火
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.29,1:10:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是山老頭啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.73,1:10:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令各隊隊長
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.86,1:10:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制止靈子的失控 是
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.76,1:10:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波盡為吾盾 雷盡為吾刃
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.37,1:10:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙魚理
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.40,1:10:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花風亂 花神啼
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.29,1:10:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天風亂天魔嗤 花天狂骨
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.12,1:10:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 碎峰 是
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.94,1:10:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬鬨
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.90,1:11:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好..
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.22,1:11:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎蜂
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.46,1:11:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴叫吧 紅姬
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.82,1:11:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜一大人 非常抱歉 夜一大人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.04,1:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事 上吧 是
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.34,1:11:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上我 是
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.16,1:12:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰輪丸
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.14,1:12:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低吟吧 灰貓
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.55,1:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,割裂吧 風死
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.41,1:12:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓親
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.61,1:12:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松本 檜佐木
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.84,1:12:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這硬家伙是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.79,1:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.08,1:13:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.76,1:13:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你啊 竟敢摸我的頭
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.56,1:13:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小劍 早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.13,1:13:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八千流 別掉下去哦 知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.48,1:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 只要能干掉這家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.55,1:14:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.19,1:14:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.16,1:14:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個男人的記憶割除
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.34,1:14:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來誰都不會記得露琪亞了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.16,1:14:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這樣就只有我們是露琪亞的珍視之人了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.54,1:14:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 記憶不是全部
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.10,1:14:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀次的靈魂記得我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.11,1:14:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞也是
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.13,1:14:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們無法奪走我們之間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.32,1:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.58,1:14:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.92,1:14:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.13,1:15:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜助
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.12,1:15:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 太大了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.11,1:15:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然若不想辦法處理實驗塔內部的裝置
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.94,1:15:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是解決不了問題的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.64,1:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有這家伙在想要接近實驗塔談何容易
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.92,1:15:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.53,1:15:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別落後了 弓親
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.00,1:15:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更木 復活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.57,1:15:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家趁現在 雖然十分困難
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.31,1:15:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要避開那家伙前往實驗塔..
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.62,1:15:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散落吧 千本櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.42,1:15:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.31,1:15:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不賴啊 白哉小子
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.01,1:15:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.63,1:15:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了 朽木隊長
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.08,1:16:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大紅蓮冰輪丸
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.20,1:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了 日番谷隊長
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.96,1:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多禮 快上
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.88,1:16:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍霰架
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.67,1:16:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也動真格的了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.10,1:16:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綻裂吧 紅姬
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.60,1:17:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 看後面 一護
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.18,1:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縛道之六十一 六杖光牢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.17,1:17:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.82,1:17:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白哉
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.95,1:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.65,1:17:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白哉
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.43,1:17:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你所言屬實
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.08,1:17:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更應由我來了結這一切
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.48,1:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.97,1:18:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞還在那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.28,1:18:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 我們都是相連的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.50,1:18:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 沒錯吧 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.29,1:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在進行靈壓的虛化
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.58,1:18:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太晚了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.64,1:18:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.59,1:18:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.49,1:18:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.26,1:18:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 救救…大姐 救救……
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.36,1:18:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救你的家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.45,1:18:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.43,1:18:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.20,1:19:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.12,1:19:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來成為死神
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.69,1:19:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能不能行
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.67,1:19:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗的話你我都會死
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.20,1:19:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為了保護我和我的家人的性命
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.05,1:19:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲了自己 用我作為賭注
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.38,1:19:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也絕對不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.84,1:19:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你自便
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.60,1:20:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,割裂他 殺死死神
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.66,1:20:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.85,1:20:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次由我來分給你力量
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.91,1:20:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快清醒吧 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.06,1:20:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑崎一護
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.23,1:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.49,1:20:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙干了什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.63,1:21:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卍解 千本櫻景嚴
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.01,1:21:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狒骨大炮
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.45,1:21:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來總算解決了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.33,1:22:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一護
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.93,1:22:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.11,1:22:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一護
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.84,1:22:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.38,1:22:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.61,1:22:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露…琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.67,1:22:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是露琪亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.25,1:22:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.17,1:22:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們遭報應了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.22,1:22:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有聽露琪亞的話
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.94,1:22:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 不要討厭我姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.41,1:22:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞救命
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.52,1:22:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.64,1:23:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.26,1:23:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.05,1:23:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.31,1:23:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.51,1:23:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們..
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.15,1:23:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.82,1:23:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.21,1:23:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞 背後
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.52,1:23:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞真厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.37,1:23:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.95,1:23:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.87,1:23:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要 你的靈力
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.60,1:23:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個身體已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.79,1:23:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.18,1:23:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是死神啊 你這怪物
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.96,1:24:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.09,1:24:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離露琪亞遠點 死神
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.87,1:24:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.32,1:24:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.00,1:24:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.45,1:24:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我醒來之後你們已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.10,1:24:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就忘了那件事
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.22,1:24:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為那只虛割除了你的記憶吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.22,1:24:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有一點因為
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.41,1:24:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩人擁有一種叫作空間轉移的特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.43,1:25:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕那兩人為了保護露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.65,1:25:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死前把虛寄生在了自己身上
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.47,1:25:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只虛匆忙逃進了虛圈
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.83,1:25:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒發現它自己寄生在了死人身上
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.37,1:25:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.94,1:25:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們將虛的意識吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.21,1:25:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且只靠想要見到露琪亞的強烈信念
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.46,1:25:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而回到此地的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.19,1:25:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想起來啦？ 對不起 我說了謊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.98,1:25:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們那時候已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.29,1:25:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會結束呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.08,1:25:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死並不代表結束
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.77,1:25:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.88,1:25:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.84,1:25:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.52,1:25:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想見露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.59,1:25:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只有露琪亞你了..
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.98,1:26:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.55,1:26:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你們來說 最珍視的人不是一直在身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.32,1:26:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起你們的名字了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.98,1:26:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焔和雫
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.58,1:26:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是背靠背相映成輝的一對
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.63,1:26:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.07,1:26:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.98,1:26:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好名字
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.76,1:26:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直想問的就是這個
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.92,1:26:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.68,1:26:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.25,1:26:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焔姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.81,1:26:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.15,1:26:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.83,1:27:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焔 雫 別走啊 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.81,1:27:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焔 雫 回答我 回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.12,1:27:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很能干吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.49,1:27:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是模仿露琪亞你
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.68,1:27:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常給我們畫的畫而畫出的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.33,1:27:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一護 你要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.55,1:27:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.48,1:28:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被你救了一次啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.01,1:28:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底最初救我的還是你..
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.40,1:28:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 如果死真的並不意味著結束的話
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.69,1:28:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們那次相遇可能並不是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.70,1:28:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能很久之前就已經彼此相連了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.90,1:28:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.56,1:28:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一旦相連的羈絆 是不是不會消失呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.45,1:28:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是這樣 即使全部忘記
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.57,1:28:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定什麼地方還會相連
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.06,1:28:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那對姐弟也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.38,1:28:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.13,1:28:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 我先回去了 死神
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.74,1:28:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是死神
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.86,1:28:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是朽木露琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.85,1:33:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.18,1:33:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽誰都不來救我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.58,1:33:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一護 你應該不會忘記的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.31,1:33:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐之後是你嗎 可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.28,1:33:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 大姐…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.85,1:33:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.68,1:33:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抛下我！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.41,1:29:08.84,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今宵月は何処を照らすの？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.03,1:29:12.35,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厚い雲に覆われた空
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.53,1:29:17.78,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今宵君は誰に抱かれているのか
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.97,1:29:25.29,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨に一人泣こうか
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.54,1:29:46.97,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全てを分かり合えると思い
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.16,1:29:50.47,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待などした自分を恥じれば
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.60,1:29:54.22,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太宰を手に屋上に上がり
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.35,1:29:58.10,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この世などはと憂いてみせる空
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.29,1:30:05.10,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,に唾を吐いたら自分にかかった
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.29,1:30:08.60,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅人気取りでいたいくせに
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.79,1:30:12.16,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷い道回り道が嫌いで
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.35,1:30:15.92,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨風しのげる屋根の下で
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.05,1:30:19.42,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,グーグル検索で世界を見る
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.61,1:30:26.43,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君に屆かず 愛の言葉
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.45,1:30:29.83,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今宵月は何処を照らすの？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.01,1:30:33.45,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厚い雲に覆われた空
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.57,1:30:35.70,aas,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}今宵君は誰に抱かれているのか
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.41,1:29:08.84,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜月亮將照亮哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.03,1:29:12.35,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃重的烏雲將天空覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.53,1:29:17.78,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜誰將擁抱著你
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.97,1:29:25.29,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還會在雨中獨自哭泣嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.54,1:29:46.97,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你為自己感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.16,1:29:50.47,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們對彼此是如此徹底的了解
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.60,1:29:54.22,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手牽著手我們坐在屋頂上
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.35,1:29:58.10,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑著那個讓世界如此悲傷的天空
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.29,1:30:05.10,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那悲傷卻降臨在我們身上
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.29,1:30:08.60,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將自己裝作一個旅者
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.79,1:30:12.16,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻迷失在你曾經憎恨的路上
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.35,1:30:15.92,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜷縮在避雨的屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.05,1:30:19.42,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搜尋般的望著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.61,1:30:26.43,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的世界沒有陪伴在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.45,1:30:29.83,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜月亮將照亮哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.01,1:30:33.45,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃重的烏雲將天空覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.57,1:30:35.70,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}今夜誰將擁抱著你
